{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":144,"text":"I've come here today"},{"time":1464,"text":"to talk to you about a problem."},{"time":4151,"text":"It's a very simple yet devastating problem,"},{"time":7678,"text":"one that spans the globe"},{"time":9623,"text":"and is affecting all of us."},{"time":12536,"text":"The problem is"},{"time":14621,"text":"anonymous companies."},{"time":17346,"text":"It sounds like a really dry and technical thing,"},{"time":19436,"text":"doesn't it?"},{"time":20492,"text":"But anonymous companies are making it difficult"},{"time":22994,"text":"and sometimes impossible"},{"time":25546,"text":"to find out"},{"time":27395,"text":"the actual human beings responsible"},{"time":30394,"text":"sometimes for really terrible crimes."},{"time":35604,"text":"So, why am I here talking to all of you?"},{"time":40646,"text":"Well, I guess I am a lifelong troublemaker"},{"time":44176,"text":"and when my parents taught my twin brother and I"},{"time":47127,"text":"to question authority,"},{"time":49033,"text":"I don't think they knew where it might lead."},{"time":51044,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":52399,"text":"And, they probably really regretted it"},{"time":54238,"text":"during my stroppy teenage years when, predictably,"},{"time":57376,"text":"I questioned their authority a lot."},{"time":59994,"text":"And a lot of my school teachers"},{"time":61589,"text":"didn't appreciate it much either."},{"time":64717,"text":"You see, since the age of about five"},{"time":66852,"text":"I've always asked the question, but why?"},{"time":70525,"text":"But why does the Earth go around the sun?"},{"time":73154,"text":"But why is blood red?"},{"time":74991,"text":"But why do I have to go to school?"},{"time":77298,"text":"But why do I have to respect the teachers"},{"time":79311,"text":"and authority?"},{"time":81178,"text":"And little did I realize"},{"time":82820,"text":"that this question would become the basis"},{"time":85598,"text":"of everything I would do."},{"time":88251,"text":"And so it was"},{"time":90006,"text":"in my twenties, a long time ago,"},{"time":92490,"text":"that one rainy Sunday afternoon in North London"},{"time":96571,"text":"I was sitting with Simon Taylor"},{"time":98360,"text":"and Patrick Alley"},{"time":100368,"text":"and we were busy stuffing envelopes"},{"time":102233,"text":"for a mail out in the office of the campaign group"},{"time":105283,"text":"where we worked at the time."},{"time":107538,"text":"And as usual, we were talking \nabout the world's problems."},{"time":111623,"text":"And in particular, we were talking about"},{"time":113437,"text":"the civil war in Cambodia."},{"time":116357,"text":"And we had talked about that \nmany, many times before."},{"time":120588,"text":"But then suddenly we stopped"},{"time":122875,"text":"and looked at each other"},{"time":124419,"text":"and said, but why don't we try and change this?"},{"time":128648,"text":"And from that slightly crazy question,"},{"time":131251,"text":"over two decades"},{"time":133093,"text":"and many campaigns later,"},{"time":135359,"text":"including alerting the world"},{"time":137150,"text":"to the problem of blood diamonds funding war,"},{"time":140366,"text":"from that crazy question,"},{"time":142427,"text":"Global Witness is now an 80-strong team"},{"time":145288,"text":"of campaigners, investigators, \njournalists and lawyers."},{"time":149810,"text":"And we're all driven by the same belief,"},{"time":152113,"text":"that change really is possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156577,"text":"So, what exactly does Global Witness do?"},{"time":159696,"text":"We investigate, we report,"},{"time":161930,"text":"to uncover the people really responsible"},{"time":164652,"text":"for funding conflict --"},{"time":166565,"text":"for stealing millions from citizens around the world,"},{"time":170076,"text":"also known as state looting,"},{"time":171913,"text":"and for destroying the environment."},{"time":174522,"text":"And then we campaign hard to \nchange the system itself."},{"time":179686,"text":"And we're doing this because \nso many of the countries"},{"time":182447,"text":"rich in natural resources"},{"time":184323,"text":"like oil or diamonds or timber"},{"time":187035,"text":"are home to some of the poorest"},{"time":189539,"text":"and most dispossessed people on the planet."},{"time":193939,"text":"And much of this injustice"},{"time":195433,"text":"is made possible"},{"time":197087,"text":"by currently accepted business practices."},{"time":200819,"text":"And one of these is anonymous companies."},{"time":205036,"text":"Now we've come up against anonymous companies"},{"time":207130,"text":"in lots of our investigations,"},{"time":209270,"text":"like in the Democratic Republic of Congo,"},{"time":211952,"text":"where we exposed how secretive deals"},{"time":214704,"text":"involving anonymous companies"},{"time":216337,"text":"had deprived the citizens"},{"time":218522,"text":"of one of the poorest countries on the planet"},{"time":222487,"text":"of well over a billion dollars."},{"time":224363,"text":"That's twice the country's health \nand education budget combined."},{"time":229894,"text":"Or in Liberia,"},{"time":231215,"text":"where an international predatory logging company"},{"time":234063,"text":"used front companies as it attempted to grab"},{"time":236626,"text":"a really huge chunk of Liberia's unique forests."},{"time":240815,"text":"Or political corruption in Sarawak, Malaysia,"},{"time":243898,"text":"which has led to the destruction \nof much of its forests."},{"time":247093,"text":"Well, that uses anonymous companies too."},{"time":251234,"text":"We secretly filmed some of the family"},{"time":253523,"text":"of the former chief minister and a lawyer"},{"time":256320,"text":"as they told our undercover investigator"},{"time":258592,"text":"exactly how these dubious deals are done"},{"time":261344,"text":"using such companies."},{"time":264420,"text":"And the awful thing is,"},{"time":266193,"text":"there are so many other examples out there"},{"time":269499,"text":"from all walks of life."},{"time":273503,"text":"This truly is a scandal of epic proportions"},{"time":277721,"text":"hidden in plain sight."},{"time":280486,"text":"Whether it's the ruthless Mexican drugs cartel,"},{"time":283265,"text":"the Zetas,"},{"time":284308,"text":"who use anonymous companies \nto launder profits"},{"time":286962,"text":"while their drugs-related violence"},{"time":288908,"text":"is tearing communities apart across the Americas."},{"time":293526,"text":"Or the anonymous company,"},{"time":295474,"text":"which bought up Americans' tax debts,"},{"time":297745,"text":"piled on the legal fees"},{"time":299537,"text":"and then gave homeowners a choice:"},{"time":300921,"text":"Pay up or lose your home."},{"time":303935,"text":"Imagine being threatened with losing your home"},{"time":306613,"text":"sometimes over a debt of just a few hundred dollars,"},{"time":309327,"text":"and not being able to find out"},{"time":310697,"text":"who you were really up against."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314233,"text":"Now anonymous companies"},{"time":315672,"text":"are great for sanctions busting too."},{"time":318546,"text":"As the Iranian government found out"},{"time":321092,"text":"when, through a series of front companies,"},{"time":322927,"text":"it owned a building in the very heart of Manhattan,"},{"time":326020,"text":"on Fifth Avenue,"},{"time":328314,"text":"despite American sanctions."},{"time":331209,"text":"And Juicy Couture, home of of the velvet track suit,"},{"time":334343,"text":"and other companies were the unwitting,"},{"time":337072,"text":"unknowing tenants there."},{"time":340179,"text":"There are just so many examples,"},{"time":342310,"text":"the horesemeat scandal in Europe,"},{"time":344766,"text":"the Italian mafia, they've used these companies"},{"time":347263,"text":"for decades."},{"time":349052,"text":"The $100 million American Medicare fraud,"},{"time":354811,"text":"the supply of weapons to wars around the world"},{"time":358583,"text":"including those"},{"time":359610,"text":"in Eastern Europe in the early '90s."},{"time":362396,"text":"Anonymous companies"},{"time":363674,"text":"have even come to light"},{"time":365330,"text":"in the recent revolution in the Ukraine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369696,"text":"But, for every case that we and others expose"},{"time":374201,"text":"there are so many more that will remain hidden away"},{"time":377418,"text":"because of the current system."},{"time":379815,"text":"And it's just a simple truth"},{"time":381774,"text":"that some of the people responsible \nfor outrageous crimes,"},{"time":386391,"text":"for stealing from you and me"},{"time":388631,"text":"and millions of others,"},{"time":390675,"text":"they are remaining faceless"},{"time":391858,"text":"and they are escaping accountability"},{"time":394343,"text":"and they're doing this with ease,"},{"time":396515,"text":"and they're doing it using legal structures."},{"time":399930,"text":"And really, that is unfair."},{"time":404951,"text":"Well, you might well ask,"},{"time":406890,"text":"what exactly is an anonymous company,"},{"time":409784,"text":"and can I really set one up, and use it,"},{"time":412192,"text":"without anyone knowing who I am?"},{"time":414920,"text":"Well, the answer is, yes you can."},{"time":416651,"text":"But if you're anything like me,"},{"time":418366,"text":"you'll want to see some of that for yourself,"},{"time":420378,"text":"so let me show you."},{"time":422086,"text":"Well first you need to work out"},{"time":423403,"text":"where you want to set it up."},{"time":425441,"text":"Now, at this point you might be imagining"},{"time":427418,"text":"one of those lovely tropical island tax havens"},{"time":430936,"text":"but here's the thing,"},{"time":432941,"text":"shockingly,"},{"time":434138,"text":"my own hometown, London,"},{"time":436482,"text":"and indeed the U.K.,"},{"time":437811,"text":"is one of the best places in the world"},{"time":440533,"text":"to set up an anonymous company."},{"time":443437,"text":"And the other, even better,"},{"time":446126,"text":"I'm afraid that's America."},{"time":450049,"text":"Do you know, in some states across America"},{"time":452505,"text":"you need less identification"},{"time":454822,"text":"to open up a company"},{"time":456289,"text":"than you do to get a library card,"},{"time":459406,"text":"like Delaware,"},{"time":460662,"text":"which is one of the easiest places"},{"time":462744,"text":"in the world to set up an anonymous company."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466983,"text":"Okay, so let's say it's America,"},{"time":468584,"text":"and let's say it's Delaware,"},{"time":470659,"text":"and now you can simply go online"},{"time":472522,"text":"and find yourself a company service provider."},{"time":475620,"text":"These are the companies that \ncan set your one up for you,"},{"time":478603,"text":"and remember, it's all legal,\nroutine business practice."},{"time":482745,"text":"So, here's one,"},{"time":484384,"text":"but there are plenty of others to choose from."},{"time":487311,"text":"And having made your choice,"},{"time":488942,"text":"you then pick what type of company you want"},{"time":491448,"text":"and then fill in a contact, name and address."},{"time":494564,"text":"But don't worry,"},{"time":495748,"text":"it doesn't have to be your name."},{"time":497307,"text":"It can be your lawyer's"},{"time":498789,"text":"or your service provider's,"},{"time":500688,"text":"and it's not for the public record anyway."},{"time":504523,"text":"And then you add the owner of the company."},{"time":507080,"text":"Now this is the key part,"},{"time":509019,"text":"and again it doesn't have to be you,"},{"time":510899,"text":"because you can get creative,"},{"time":513002,"text":"because there is a whole universe \nout there of nominees"},{"time":516551,"text":"to choose from."},{"time":518398,"text":"And nominees are the people that you"},{"time":520734,"text":"can legally pay to be your company's owner."},{"time":525570,"text":"And if you don't want to involve anyone else,"},{"time":527412,"text":"it doesn't even have to be an actual human being."},{"time":530275,"text":"It could be another company."},{"time":533363,"text":"And then finally,"},{"time":534793,"text":"give your company a name"},{"time":536522,"text":"add a few more details and make your payment."},{"time":539253,"text":"And then the service provider"},{"time":540673,"text":"will take a few hours or more to process it."},{"time":543456,"text":"But there you are,"},{"time":544695,"text":"in 10 minutes of online shopping"},{"time":547075,"text":"you can create yourself an anonymous company."},{"time":551289,"text":"And not only is it easy,"},{"time":552677,"text":"really, really easy and cheap,"},{"time":555284,"text":"it's totally legal too."},{"time":557572,"text":"But the fun doesn't have to end there,"},{"time":561296,"text":"maybe you want to be even more anonymous."},{"time":564095,"text":"Well, that's no problem either."},{"time":566198,"text":"You can simply keep adding layers,"},{"time":568956,"text":"companies owned by companies."},{"time":571056,"text":"You can have hundreds of layers"},{"time":572436,"text":"with hundreds of companies spread across"},{"time":574524,"text":"lots of different countries,"},{"time":577181,"text":"like a giant web,"},{"time":578511,"text":"each layer adds anonymity."},{"time":580700,"text":"Each layer makes it more difficult"},{"time":582930,"text":"for law enforcement and others"},{"time":584619,"text":"to find out who the real owner is."},{"time":588002,"text":"But whose interests is this all serving?"},{"time":592092,"text":"It might be in the interests of the company"},{"time":594218,"text":"or a particular individual,"},{"time":595984,"text":"but what about all of us, the public?"},{"time":598372,"text":"There hasn't even been a global conversation yet"},{"time":601141,"text":"about whether it's okay"},{"time":602561,"text":"to misuse companies in this way."},{"time":605796,"text":"And what does it all mean for us?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":609674,"text":"Well, an example that really haunts me"},{"time":612227,"text":"is one I came across recently."},{"time":614605,"text":"And it's that of a horrific fire"},{"time":616554,"text":"in a nightclub in Buenos Aires"},{"time":618339,"text":"about a decade ago."},{"time":621290,"text":"It was the night before New Year's Eve."},{"time":623560,"text":"Three thousand very happy revelers,"},{"time":625728,"text":"many of them teenagers,"},{"time":626765,"text":"were crammed into a space meant for 1,000."},{"time":629960,"text":"And then tragedy struck,"},{"time":631133,"text":"a fire broke out"},{"time":632736,"text":"plastic decorations were melting from the ceiling"},{"time":634820,"text":"and toxic smoke filled the club."},{"time":636796,"text":"So people tried to escape"},{"time":638861,"text":"only to find that some of the fire doors"},{"time":641494,"text":"had been chained shut."},{"time":645155,"text":"Over 200 people died."},{"time":647588,"text":"Seven hundred were injured trying to get out."},{"time":651347,"text":"And as the victims' families \nand the city and the country"},{"time":654892,"text":"reeled in shock,"},{"time":656436,"text":"investigators tried to find out who was responsible."},{"time":659982,"text":"And as they looked for the owners of the club,"},{"time":662473,"text":"they found instead anonymous companies,"},{"time":666031,"text":"and confusion surrounded the identities of those"},{"time":668325,"text":"involved with the companies."},{"time":670832,"text":"Now ultimately, a range of people were charged"},{"time":673294,"text":"and some went to jail."},{"time":675321,"text":"But this was an awful tragedy,"},{"time":677154,"text":"and it shouldn't have been so difficult"},{"time":679137,"text":"just to try and find out who was responsible"},{"time":683047,"text":"for those deaths."},{"time":686008,"text":"Because in an age"},{"time":687953,"text":"when there is so much information"},{"time":690207,"text":"out there in the open,"},{"time":692204,"text":"why should this crucial information"},{"time":693878,"text":"about company ownership"},{"time":695388,"text":"stay hidden away?"},{"time":697094,"text":"Why should tax evaders, corrupt \ngovernment officials,"},{"time":700819,"text":"arms traders and more,"},{"time":703071,"text":"be able to hide their identities from us, the public?"},{"time":707109,"text":"Why should this secrecy be such \nan accepted business practice?"},{"time":712738,"text":"Anonymous companies"},{"time":714426,"text":"might be the norm right now"},{"time":716635,"text":"but it wasn't always this way."},{"time":718641,"text":"Companies were created"},{"time":720438,"text":"to give people a chance to innovate"},{"time":722710,"text":"and not have to put everything on the line."},{"time":726373,"text":"Companies were created to limit financial risk,"},{"time":729715,"text":"they were never intended to \nbe used as a moral shield."},{"time":734665,"text":"Companies were never intended to be anonymous,"},{"time":736939,"text":"and they don't have to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":739355,"text":"And so I come to my wish."},{"time":742245,"text":"My wish is for us to know"},{"time":745046,"text":"who owns and controls companies"},{"time":747772,"text":"so that they can no longer be used anonymously"},{"time":750522,"text":"against the public good."},{"time":753152,"text":"Together let's ignite world opinion,"},{"time":755818,"text":"change the law,"},{"time":757295,"text":"and launch a new era of openness in business."},{"time":762175,"text":"So what might this look like?"},{"time":763807,"text":"Well, imagine if you could go online"},{"time":766376,"text":"and look up the real owner of a company."},{"time":769493,"text":"Imagine if this data were open and free,"},{"time":772265,"text":"accessible across borders"},{"time":773976,"text":"for citizens and businesses"},{"time":775775,"text":"and law enforcement alike."},{"time":777463,"text":"Imagine what a game changer that would be."},{"time":781931,"text":"So how are we going to do this?"},{"time":784434,"text":"Well, there is only one way."},{"time":785880,"text":"Together, we have to change the law globally"},{"time":789131,"text":"to create public registries"},{"time":791072,"text":"which list the true owners of companies"},{"time":793927,"text":"and can be accessed by all"},{"time":795963,"text":"with no loopholes."},{"time":798092,"text":"And yes, this is ambitious,"},{"time":801824,"text":"but there is momentum on this issue,"},{"time":804215,"text":"and over the years I have seen"},{"time":806259,"text":"the sheer power of momentum,"},{"time":808591,"text":"and it's just starting on this issue."},{"time":810975,"text":"There is such an opportunity right now."},{"time":814253,"text":"And the TED community"},{"time":816282,"text":"of creative and innovative thinkers and doers"},{"time":819647,"text":"across all of society"},{"time":821544,"text":"could make the crucial difference."},{"time":824803,"text":"You really can make this change happen."},{"time":828637,"text":"Now, a simple starting point"},{"time":830439,"text":"is the address behind me"},{"time":831905,"text":"for a Facebook page that you can join now"},{"time":834264,"text":"to support the campaign and spread the word."},{"time":837010,"text":"It's going to be a springboard"},{"time":838434,"text":"for our global campaigning."},{"time":840395,"text":"And the techies among you,"},{"time":841870,"text":"you could really help us create a prototype"},{"time":845243,"text":"public registry"},{"time":846963,"text":"to demonstrate what a powerful tool this could be."},{"time":851839,"text":"Campaign groups from around the world"},{"time":854350,"text":"have come together to work on this issue."},{"time":859210,"text":"The U.K. government is already on board;"},{"time":862490,"text":"it supports these public registries."},{"time":864892,"text":"And just last week,"},{"time":866790,"text":"the European Parliament came on board"},{"time":869498,"text":"with a vote 600 to 30 in favor of public registries."},{"time":874564,"text":"That is momentum."},{"time":876989,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":881985,"text":"But it's early days."},{"time":884290,"text":"America still needs to come on board,"},{"time":886782,"text":"as do so many other countries."},{"time":890359,"text":"And to succeed we will all together"},{"time":893468,"text":"need to help and push our politicians,"},{"time":895912,"text":"because without that,"},{"time":897499,"text":"real far-reaching, world-shifting change"},{"time":899467,"text":"just isn't going to happen."},{"time":902168,"text":"Because this isn't just about changing the law,"},{"time":904857,"text":"this is about starting a conversation"},{"time":906949,"text":"about what it's okay for companies to do,"},{"time":909342,"text":"and in what ways is it acceptable \nto use company structures."},{"time":914376,"text":"This isn't just a dry policy issue."},{"time":917149,"text":"This is a human issue"},{"time":918637,"text":"which affects us all."},{"time":921295,"text":"This is about being on the right side of history."},{"time":927699,"text":"Global citizens, innovators, \nbusiness leaders, individuals,"},{"time":933057,"text":"we need you."},{"time":935044,"text":"Together, let's kickstart this global movement."},{"time":938554,"text":"Let's just do it,"},{"time":939899,"text":"let's end anonymous companies."},{"time":943201,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":945305,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}